    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048300/extras/43952d8e083999cdf9e85d2cd263eff7.poster.avif?t=1757693125\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048300/extras/43952d8e083999cdf9e85d2cd263eff7.webm?t=1757693125\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048300/extras/43952d8e083999cdf9e85d2cd263eff7.mp4?t=1757693125\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >双食》是一款适合在周末玩的短篇地牢爬行游戏，它以回合制战斗和取巧的方式进行。玩家将抵挡卡牌，用强大的日蚀卡牌扭转战局，并掠夺怪物来升级他们的卡组。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家将扮演三个角色中的一个，探索神秘的地牢，躲避危险的陷阱，发掘强大的宝藏，探寻秘密。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>独特的取巧战斗</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048300/extras/c12f5b7adb01f40d6b227f3bdf567aef.poster.avif?t=1757693125\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048300/extras/c12f5b7adb01f40d6b227f3bdf567aef.webm?t=1757693125\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048300/extras/c12f5b7adb01f40d6b227f3bdf567aef.mp4?t=1757693125\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗是通过 “取巧 ”来解决的！就像用纸牌击剑一样！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在战斗中，玩家和敌人都能控制获胜条件，因此每次遭遇战都会带来战略抉择。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特的组合能带来有趣的选择和动态的战斗。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用功能强大的日蚀卡切换月亮和太阳，从而改变战局。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >招架卡！提供高风险、高回报机会的战术选择。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>升级你的卡组，变得更强</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048300/extras/01bdb675d6208de2590159c46f23ec4f.poster.avif?t=1757693125\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048300/extras/01bdb675d6208de2590159c46f23ec4f.webm?t=1757693125\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048300/extras/01bdb675d6208de2590159c46f23ec4f.mp4?t=1757693125\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >击败敌人收集新卡，找到宝藏获得新力量。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >获得强大的能力和强化。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >提升等级，专精等级，打造符合自己风格的游戏方式。</p></li></ul>",
